#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.model_selection.KFold.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.model\\_selection.KFold"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:1 of
msgid "K-Folds cross-validator"
msgstr "K 折交叉验证器"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:3 of
msgid ""
"Provides train/test indices to split data in train/test sets. Split "
"dataset into k consecutive folds (without shuffling by default)."
msgstr ""
"提供训练/测试索引以将数据划分为训练集和测试集。默认情况下将数据集分割为 k"
" 个连续的折（不打乱顺序）。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:6 of
msgid ""
"Each fold is then used once as a validation while the k - 1 remaining "
"folds form the training set."
msgstr "每一轮中使用一个折作为验证集，而其余的 k - 1 个折组成训练集。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.model_selection.KFold.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:9 of
msgid ""
"Number of folds. Must be at least 2.  .. versionchanged:: 0.22     "
"``n_splits`` default value changed from 3 to 5."
msgstr ""
"折数。必须至少为 2。 .. versionchanged:: 0.22 ``n_splits`` 默认值从 3 "
"改为 5。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:9 of
msgid "Number of folds. Must be at least 2."
msgstr "折数。必须至少为2。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:11 of
msgid "``n_splits`` default value changed from 3 to 5."
msgstr "``n_splits`` 默认值从3改为5。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:14 of
msgid ""
"Whether to shuffle the data before splitting into batches. Note that the "
"samples within each split will not be shuffled."
msgstr "是否在分割成批次之前打乱数据。注意，每个分割中的样本不会被打乱。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:17 of
msgid ""
"When `shuffle` is True, `random_state` affects the ordering of the "
"indices, which controls the randomness of each fold. Otherwise, this "
"parameter has no effect. Pass an int for reproducible output across "
"multiple function calls. See :term:`Glossary <random_state>`."
msgstr ""
"当 `shuffle` 为 True 时，`random_state` 会影响索引的排序，从而控制每一折"
"的随机性。否则此参数无效。传递一个整数可在多次函数调用中产生可重现的结果"
"。参见 :term:`术语表 <random_state>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:25 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:43 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:44 of
msgid ""
"The first ``n_samples % n_splits`` folds have size ``n_samples // "
"n_splits + 1``, other folds have size ``n_samples // n_splits``, where "
"``n_samples`` is the number of samples."
msgstr ""
"前 ``n_samples % n_splits`` 个折的大小为 ``n_samples // n_splits + 1``，"
"其余折的大小为 ``n_samples // n_splits``，其中 ``n_samples`` 是样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:48 of
msgid ""
"Randomized CV splitters may return different results for each call of "
"split. You can make the results identical by setting `random_state` to an"
" integer."
msgstr ""
"随机化的交叉验证分割器在每次调用 split 时可能返回不同的结果。你可以通过将"
" `random_state` 设置为一个整数来使结果一致。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:54 of
msgid ":py:obj:`StratifiedKFold`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:55 of
msgid ""
"Takes group information into account to avoid building folds with "
"imbalanced class distributions (for binary or multiclass classification "
"tasks)."
msgstr "考虑到类别信息，避免构建具有不平衡类别分布的折（用于二分类或多分类任务）。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:57 of
msgid ":py:obj:`GroupKFold`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:58 of
msgid "K-fold iterator variant with non-overlapping groups."
msgstr "非重叠组的 K 折迭代器变体。"

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:60 of
msgid ":py:obj:`RepeatedKFold`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.model_selection._split.KFold:61 of
msgid "Repeats K-Fold n times."
msgstr "重复 K 折 n 次。"

